Finally got around to editing the footage from our anniversary trip to the Bahamas and Mexico.
.
What started off as a 4 day Bahamas cruise, turned into a 7-day Mexican cruise due to hurricane Dorian.
.
Our first stop in Nassau was awesome, we went to a private beach island where we got to swim, snorkel, and see some dolphins, sea lions, and manta rays. .
After that, we visited Costa Maya and Cozumel Mexico and was able to see a luchador fight, have fish eat the dead skin off our feet, and go snorkeling and saw some cool fish! On a side note, the coral in Mexico is very sad looking. .
A couple extra days on the cruise ship were great. Lots of food, good shows, fun in the casino, etc
.
Overall it was a great trip! And I‚Äôm so happy that @guarango and @jessicamarie00 could come celebrate their own anniversary with us on the same trip. ‚Ä¢
